SUMMARY:Toronto Electronics Meetup
DESCRIPTION:Learn\, build\, repair\, repeat!\n\n\nAre you interested in how things work? Working on a project and looking for people to brainstorm with? Interested in helping others to solve problems or repair circuits? We meet on the second Wednesday of each month at Site 3 Colaboratory in downtown Toronto.  \nMeetings are free for Site 3 members\, and PWYC for non-members. All donations help us cover facilities and parts.  \nTypically we do a round of intros\, talk about and show our current projects\, help any new people with questions and then get into our builds or a topic.
URL:https://www.site3.ca/event/toronto-electronics-meetup-5/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.site3.ca/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5987_image.png
END:VEVENT
